title: Ep. - 310 - ETHAN AND OLIVIA PLATH FROM WELCOME TO PLATHVILLE
description:
Ethan and Olivia Plath from TLC’s Welcome to Plathville about parents who are raising their nine kids in rural Georgia on a small farm. Barry Plath and wife Kim wanted to shelter their children from the dangers of the real world, and have restricted access to TV, radio, video games, and the internet. Ethan and Olivia talk about growing up in strict homes, their complicated relationship with his family, and their marriage.
